These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, epic, musical, adventure, western, family, time-travel
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, d&b, salsa, trance, indie, ambient, funk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, skiing, baseball, sailing, soccer, cycling, basketball
 1. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the fan of d&b and the fan of country##2
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the fan of trance is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person watching western movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of salsa##1
11. the fan of ambient is the person watching adventure movies##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
13. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of indie##1
14. the person watching family movies is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | animation     | family | epic | adventure | time-travel  | musical  |
| Music-Genre   | country  | trance        | d&b  | funk     | ambient   | salsa       | indie   |
| Sport         | skiing   | basketball | sailing    | baseball  | soccer | cycling | snowboarding |

