.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: french, spanish, indonesian, brazilian, american, argentine, pakistani
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, cycling, surfing, skiing, lacrosse, tennis, skateboarding
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, snowmobile, helicopter, skateboard, taxi, tram
 1. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is the pakistani##1
 6. the french is the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the french is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person driving the tram##2
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the american##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the indonesian is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the american is on the right of the french##1
12. the person driving the airplane is the spanish##1
13. the brazilian is on the left of the french##1
14. the brazilian is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
15. the spanish is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | argentine | pakistani      | brazilian     | french  | american | indonesian | spanish |
| Sport         | cycling  | golf | tennis | surfing | skateboarding | skiing   | lacrosse  |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | taxi     | tram        | helicopter  | skateboard   | motorbike       | airplane      |

