 1. the person driving the train is the freelancer##1
 2. the person driving the subway is the mechanic##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the paramedic##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the bus and the chef##2
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the chef##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
10. the nurse is on the right of the police-officer##1
11. the person driving the train is the freelancer##1
12. the nurse is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the mechanic##1
14. the person driving the bus is the person drinking mirinda##1
15. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
