10. the canadian is the person eating nectarine##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is the nigerian##1
12. the person eating pear is the chinese##1
13. the argentine is on the far right##1
14. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
