10. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is chess##1
