.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  nurse, electrician, lawyer, doctor, accountant, entrepreneur, firefighter
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, soul, gospel, rock, country, disco, classical
7 different pets are kept: lizard, hamster, pony, goat, goldfish, dog, cat
 1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the lawyer##1
 2. the owner of the dog is between the fan of country and the fan of gospel##2
 3. the fan of r&b is the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the fan of classical is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the nurse##1
 6. the lawyer is in the middle##1
 7. the accountant is the fan of disco##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the fan of r&b is the owner of the hamster##1
10. the firefighter is the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the nurse is on the right of the doctor##1
12. the fan of classical is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
14. the fan of soul is on the left of the nurse##1
15. the firefighter is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | electrician | entrepreneur | accountant | lawyer  | firefighter   | doctor | nurse      |
| Music-Genre   | classical | gospel        | disco    | country     | rock     | soul   | r&b        |
| Pet           | lizard   | pony       | dog    | goat | goldfish | cat   | hamster |

