10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the owner of the mouse and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
